        Selling a Brisbane Property with an Existing Mortgage: What the Process Involves
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Having a mortgage on your property when you sell is entirely normal. Here is how the discharge process works in practice, what to prepare for, and where things can get complicated.
      </p>
